{"tid":1381474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩理由過埋728都未簽爆名？","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:49:55.000Z","uid":76365,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff09414fb6848acb855b310b12c924cf62fbba8","tid":1381474,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"到今日4:30都係得唔夠兩萬人簽，deadline 4/8，我地對唔對得住咁多受傷嘅義士？<br />\n<br />\n你話一個月前612警渣射頭只係個別事件，我都算，但依家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班警渣用緊嘅武器已經升晒級，仲要無視原廠使用指引，槍槍打頭！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再係咁落去我地仲有幾多人可以喺前線？我地嘅人力物力仲可以幫幾多義士睇病打官司？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">義士唔係condom!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要救義士，可以從對家裝備入手。我唔保證簽完美國會做嘢，但你唔簽嘅話，就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連未來嘅義士們都一定會處於水深火熱之中！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【白宮聯署：美國應該停止出口人群管制裝備予香港警察】<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=74e3bf78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-calling-suspension-crowd-control-equipment-exports-hong-kong-prevent-human-rights-abuses</a><br />\n<br />\n想知更多:<br />\n黃之鋒 Joshua Wong：到底昨日我地俾乜野子彈射中？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380814</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d57bf2c32fdf41a2fff26e4d97b1f26ddd5e65f7","tid":1381474,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"記住verify signa